    "description": "<blockquote><p><strong>Requirements: </strong>you must have mastered the <strong>Darkblade </strong>Class.</p></blockquote><p>When you hit a creature with an attack, if that attack <strong>only </strong>targeted that creature and you have a <strong>Bond </strong>towards them, you may choose to spend half of your current Hit Points, rounded down. If you do, the attack deals extra damage equal to <strong>【10 multiplied by the strength of your Bond towards the target】</strong>.</p><p>You may use this Skill only on your turn during a conflict, and <strong>only once per turn</strong>.</p><hr /><ul><li><p><strong>You Lose:</strong> @LOSS[@source.level.value/2 hp]</p></li><li><p><strong>Target Loses:</strong> @DMG[10 untyped]{1 Bond: 10 Untyped}, @DMG[20 untyped]{2 Bond: 20 Untyped}, or @DMG[30 untyped]{3 Bond: 30 Untyped}</p></li></ul>",
